rows.label: qst201105_0010
rows.name: ...As expected, there's no one here.

rows.label: qst201105_0020
rows.name:
Well, just like before, they're
probably watching from somewhere.

rows.label: qst201105_0030
rows.name:
I know you can hear me! Stop hiding
and show yourself, you coward!

rows.label: qst201105_0040
rows.name: The same thing again...

rows.label: qst201105_0050
rows.name:
There's some meaning to
this spear, isn't there?

rows.label: qst201105_0060
rows.name:
Instead of being so roundabout,
why not just talk to us directly?

rows.label: qst201105_0070
rows.name: Or are you afraid of me?

rows.label: qst201105_0075
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]

rows.label: qst201105_0080
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]?!

rows.label: qst201105_0090
rows.name: That's her, the Blade from that time.

rows.label: qst201105_0100
rows.name:
Yes, no doubt about it. One
of the Core Crystal hunters.

rows.label: qst201105_0110
rows.name: She was called Seori, right?

rows.label: qst201105_0120
rows.name: ...So it was you after all.

rows.label: qst201105_0130
rows.name:
You were meddling with us during the
monster battles too, weren't you?

rows.label: qst201105_0140
rows.name: What is your intention?

rows.label: qst201105_0150
rows.name:
You have something you want
to say to me, don't you?

rows.label: qst201105_0160
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]...

rows.label: qst201105_0170
rows.name:
You wrote that the reward was memories, but I
don't feel any meaning in what you've done.

rows.label: qst201105_0180
rows.name:
I'm done following your
random instructions.

rows.label: qst201105_0190
rows.name: So it didn't work after all...

rows.label: qst201105_0200
rows.name: What? Say it clearly.

rows.label: qst201105_0210
rows.name: ...*sigh*

rows.label: qst201105_0220
rows.name:
...Look at the message.
This is the last one.

rows.label: qst201105_0230
rows.name: Hey.
